  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently, we don't check if our eth1 endpoint is pointing to the expected eth1 network. \r\nFor e.g. if our eth1 endpoint is a mainnet node instead of goerli, we search for non-existent deposit logs in the mainnet contract from the deposit contract deploy block until current block number.\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nSearches for non existent deposit logs on the wrong eth1 network.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nShould exit the eth1 task or lighthouse process if provided an eth1 endpoint with incorrect network id.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nUse the [`net_version`](https://eth.wiki/json-rpc/API) endpoint to query the network id of the eth1 endpoint and exit if on the incorrect network.",
